Hi,

requesting help (ESC h) for /bin/ls is ugly, because man gets called with
/bin/ls as agument and tries to view the binary file. Please, add this
line at the beginning of /usr/share/zsh/functions/Misc/run-help

    1=${1##*/}

Bye, Jörg.
